@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.02 * tmp + 0.74) + 0.32))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v0) * ((v2 + 0.45 - v1 + 0.28) - v0))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.14 / v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.03 * v1 + 0.80)) + 0.78)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.83)) + ((v2 + 0.14 * v1 + 0.86) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.92)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.80)) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.24 / v2 + 0.52)))
    v0 = 0.04
    data[tid] = v0
